pageProduct.name: QV Intensive Moisturiser 100G
pageProduct.description:
General Information

QV Intensive Body Moisturiser is a highly emollient intensive moisturiser to relieve soothe and protect dry skin.  QV Intensive Body Moisturiser is water free so it won't sting when applied to inflamed or cracked skin. Suitable for dry, sensitive, itching skin and eczema.Fragrance and colour free.Propylene glycol and lanolin free.Preservative free.Easily absorbed.Dermatologists recommend.Soap free.Sting free formula.Dermatologically tested.Non-comedogenic - won't block pores.

Warnings

For external use only.  Avoid eyes.

Common Uses

Highly emollient intensive moisturiser to relieve soothe and protect dry skin.Suitable for dry, sensitive, itching skin and eczema.

Ingredients

Light liquid paraffin (paraffinum liquidum), petrolatum, isopropyl myristate, polyethylene, cetearyl alcohol, silica, dimethicone, bht.

Directions

Apply liberally to the face and body and massage in gently. Use after bathing and showering.  Use in conjunction with QV Intensive Moistsurising Cleanser.
